last_episode_to_air.overview: Warren's family-packed car breaks down following an altercation en route to Anne's Auntie Faye's funeral. Stuck on the motorway with his annoying family, Warren's day couldn't get any worse.

name: Warren
overview: Warren Thompson just wants an easy life, but thanks to his naturally difficult personality, he’s constantly finding himself in sticky situations.

episodes.name: The Pond
episodes.overview: Warren pushes Charlie into getting a job in the local garden centre so he can get a discounted pond liner.

episodes.name: The Rival
episodes.overview: Warren’s business is not going well, whilst rival driving instructor Daz's business is booming. Warren sets about reinventing himself, but his plans get scuppered.

episodes.name: The Tax Return
episodes.overview: When Warren's marital advice to brother-in-law Colin backfires, he is forced to take him in. Fortunately, Colin has a raft of hidden and very useful talents.

episodes.name: The Father Figure
episodes.overview: Warren coaches Danny in the ways of love, and also buys himself a couple of chickens, causing next door neighbour Ian to become increasingly irritated.

episodes.name: The Holiday
episodes.overview: Warren's weekend away with Anne and her mum and Dad is blighted by a raucous hen party. To make matters worse, he's worried about what Charlie and Danny are up to back home - with good reason.

episodes.name: The Funeral
episodes.overview: Warren's family-packed car breaks down following an altercation en route to Anne's Auntie Faye's funeral. Stuck on the motorway with his annoying family, Warren's day couldn't get any worse.
